    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (tmp / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.76) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.27)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.87) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.70)) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.83 * v0 + 0.04)))
    v1 = (v0 / wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.40)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.43)) - v2)
    v1 = 0.94
    data[tid] = v0
